section.rule:
Write the questions to the comment queue so they appear as github-actions[bot]
on the GitHub issue. Append an entry to .github/comment-queue.json:

  {"issue": {number}, "body": "This issue needs clarification before autonomous execution:\n\n{numbered list of specific questions}\n\nThis issue is labeled autonomously-nightly but cannot proceed without answers to the above.\nOnce resolved, re-run the nightly workflow or remove the label and work on it manually."}
